<ToolLayout
  title="Privacy"
  description="This site is privacy-first: no tracking, no cookies, no server-side processing."
>
  <h2>What we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Nothing by default. No analytics, no tracking pixels, no fingerprinting.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What happens to your input</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Tools run locally in your browser.</li>
    <li>Your input is not sent to a server by this site.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Third parties</h2>
  <p>
    This site is served as static files. If you enable third-party services in the future,
    this page will be updated.
  </p>
</ToolLayout>

